 the existing `Bearer` token structure from `lib/api-auth.ts`.\n* **RBAC Enforcement**:\n  - Administrators/Operators (`gff_admin`) can view, filter, assign, comment on, and modify all tickets.\n  - Clients can only view, filter, comment on, and modify tickets belonging to their own `client_id`. They can only create tickets bound to their own `client_id`.\n* **Backend Validation Checks"}}
